info.author: Getpaid Community
info.description:
This package contains ogone payment processor functionality for the
getpaid framework.


=======
CHANGES
=======

0.3 (2009-03-13)
----------------

- fix options location [jefroche]
- pass layout properties to ogone [jefroche]
- pep8 [jefroche]
- Add buildout files and general text documents to project root [fairwinds.dp]
- Updated proper licensing for package [fairwinds.dp]


0.2 (2008-08-23)
----------------

- Eggified package
- Added buildout files and general text documents to project root.

Detailed Documentation
**********************

This package requires:

    * zc.table [installed in lib/python] (svn://svn.zope.org/repos/main/zc.table/tags/zc.table-0.5.1/src/zc/table)
    * zc.resourcelibrary [installed in lib/python] (svn://svn.zope.org/repos/main/zc.resourcelibrary/tags/zc.resourcelibrary-0.5/src/zc/resourcelibrary)
    * Five 1.4.2 [installed in Products] (svn://svn.zope.org/repos/main/Products.Five/tags/1.4.2/)
    * CMFOnFive [installed in Products] (http://codespeak.net/svn/z3/CMFonFive/trunk)
    * five.intid [installed in lib/python] (https://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/five.intid/trunk/five)
    * Plone 2.5
    * hurry.workflow [installed in lib/python] (http://getpaid.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/vendor/hurry.workflow/branches/0.9/src/hurry/workflow)
    * ore.member [installed in lib/python] (https://svn.objectrealms.net/svn/public/ore.member/trunk/src/ore/member)
    * ore.viewlet [installed in lib/python] (https://svn.objectrealms.net/svn/public/ore.viewlet/trunk/src/ore/viewlet)
    * getpaid.core [installed in lib/python] (http://getpaid.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/getpaid.core/src/getpaid/core)
    * yoma.layout [installed in lib/python] (http://getpaid.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/vendor/yoma.layout/)
    * yoma.batching [installed in lib/python] (http://getpaid.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/vendor/yoma.batching)
    * PloneGetPaid [installed in Products] (http://getpaid.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/products/PloneGetPaid)

This package must be installed in $YourZopeInstance/lib/python/getpaid with the name ogone

Download
